<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4535044>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIG. 24. — A-F, Laxifenestella kondrovensis (Schulga-Nesterenko, 1955); A-D, tangential section showing autozooecial apertures and low median keel with nodes (arrows), SMF 21.912; E, mid-tangential section showing autozooecial chambers with hemisepta, SMF 21.912; F, mid-tangential section showing autozooecial chambers with hemisepta, SMF 21.914. G-I, Fabifenestella macrofenestrata n. sp., holotype SMF 21.915; G-H, mid-tangential section showing autozooecial chambers with hemisepta (arrow); I, tangential section showing keel nodes (arrow). Scale bars: A, G, 2 mm; B, C, E, F, 1 mm; D, 0.2 mm; H, I, 0.5 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4535044/files/figure.png" .

